"套用於當前序列。如果選擇此選項，將在工作目錄中以.png 格式生成圖表：GNUplot 視"
"窗將不會出現。此模式自動啟用“將圖表另存為.png”選項。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:146
msgid "Save plot as .png"
msgstr "將圖表另存為 png"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:147
msgid ""
"Saves the plot in .png format as well as opening the plot window. Sequence "
"working relies on this so if this option is deactivated, sequence working "
"will be deactivated too."
msgstr ""
"以.png 格式儲存圖表，並開啟 GNUplot 視窗。序列工作依賴於此，因此如果禁用此選"
"項，序列工作也將停用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:158
msgid "Measure in pixels"
msgstr "以像素為單位進行測量"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:159
msgid ""
"Measurements and the plot x axis will show distance in pixels. This option "
"is overridden if spectrometry data is set."
msgstr ""
"測量值和圖表 x 軸將以像素為單位顯示距離。如果設定了光譜資料，則此選項將被覆"
"蓋。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:170
msgid "Measure in arcsec"
msgstr "以角秒為單位進行測量"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:171
msgid ""
"If possible, measurements and the plot x axis will show distance in arcsec. "
"This requires telescope focal length and sensor pixel size metadata in the "
"FITS header. This option is overridden if spectrometry data is set."
msgstr ""
"如果可能，測量值和圖表 x 軸將以角秒為單位顯示距離。這需要 FITS 標頭中的望遠鏡"
"焦距和感測器像素尺寸後設資料。如果設定了光譜資料，則此選項將被覆蓋。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:183
msgid ""
"Generates 3 parallel intensity profiles separated by a given number of "
"pixels. Tri-profiles always plot luminance along each profile and do not use "
"spectrometric data."
msgstr ""
"生成三條平行的強度分佈曲線，按指定的像素間隔分隔。三重分佈曲線始終沿每條分佈"
"曲線繪製亮度值，且不使用光譜資料。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:194
msgid "Tri-Profile offset (px)"
msgstr "三重分佈曲線的偏移量（像素）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:208 src/gui-gtk4/cut.c:90
#: src/gui-gtk4/cut.c:127 src/gui-gtk4/cut.c:1292
msgid "Intensity Profile"
msgstr "亮度曲線"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:209
msgid ""
"Sets a custom title for the plot. If the title ends with (), if a sequence "
"is processed the current image number / total will be added inside the "
"brackets (e.g. Title (1/n))."
msgstr ""
"設定圖表的自定義標題。如果標題以 （） 結尾，如果處理序列，則當前影像編號/總數"
"將新增到括號內（例如標題 （1/n））。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_dialog.ui:214
msgid "Plot Title"
msgstr "圖表標題"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:72
msgid "Profile width / px"
msgstr "曲線寬度 / 像素"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:83
msgid ""
"Set the width of the cut. The median pixel value perpendicular to the cut "
"will be used."
msgstr "設定剪下的寬度。將使用垂直於剪下的中值像素值。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:94
msgid "Pick point 1"
msgstr "選取點 1"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:96
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:109
msgid ""
"Pick a point on the profile line corresponding to a known wavelength / "
"wavenumber. Typically this would be a known spectral line or, for true "
"spectrograph images, the start or central wavelength / wavenumber. Note: "
"these points snap to the profile line and are reset if the profile line is "
"moved."
msgstr ""
"在曲線上選取與已知波長/波數相對應的點。通常，這將是已知的譜線，或者對於真實的"
"光譜儀影像，起始或中心波長/波數。注意：這些點會吸附到曲線，並在移動曲線時重"
"設。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:107
msgid "Pick point 2"
msgstr "選取點 2"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:123
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:137
msgid "Enter the wavenumber corresponding to the selected point"
msgstr "輸入所選點對應的波數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:200
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:213
msgid ""
"This is a convenience function to allow a known wavelength to be entered "
"instead of wavenumbers. Since wavenumber is required for the plot x axis, "
"the value entered will be converted to wavenumber"
msgstr ""
"這是一個方便的功能，允許輸入已知波長而不是波數。由於圖表 x 軸需要波數，因此輸"
"入的值將轉換為波數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:223
msgid "wavelength / nm"
msgstr "波長 / nm"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:232
msgid "wavenumber / cm<sup>-1</sup>"
msgstr "波數 / cm<sup>-1</sup>"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:233
msgid "The wavenumber is the spatial frequency 1 / λ"
msgstr "波數為空間頻率 1/λ"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:243
msgid "Plot x axis"
msgstr "圖表 X 軸"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:255
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/s_pcc_dialog.ui:445
msgid "Wavelength"
msgstr "波長"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:256
msgid "Wavenumber"
msgstr "波數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:261
msgid ""
"When plotting a spectrogram, should the x axis show wavenumber or wavelength?"
msgstr "繪製光譜圖時，x 軸應該顯示波數還是波長？"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:273
msgid "Spectroscopic Calibration Points"
msgstr "光譜法校正點"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:293
msgid "Polynomial degree"
msgstr "多項式的次數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:304
msgid ""
"Sets the degree of polynomial used for background fitting, between 1 (linear "
"fit) and 6 (sextic polynomial)"
msgstr "設定用於背景擬合的多項式的次數，範圍 1（線性）到 6（六次多項式）之間"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:316
msgid "Plot measured and modelled background"
msgstr "將測量並模型化的背景繪製為圖表"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:329
msgid "Background Removal"
msgstr "背景去除"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/cut_spectroscopy_dialog.ui:374
msgid "Spectrometry"
msgstr "光譜"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/data_dialog.ui:52
msgid "More details..."
msgstr "更多…"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:44
msgid "Remove salt and pepper noise"
msgstr "移除椒鹽雜訊"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:45
msgid ""
"This option applies cosmetic correction to remove salt and pepper noise "
"before the primary denoising algorithm. This is generally a good thing and "
"the setting defaults to active."
msgstr ""
"此選項在主降雜訊演算法之前套用壞點修正以消除椒鹽雜訊。通常有益無害，預設啟"
"用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:64
msgid "Independent Channels"
msgstr "獨立通道"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:65
msgid ""
"Suppresses blocky colour artefacts that may rarely appear in colour images. "
"This option treats each channel separately and eliminates artefacts at the "
"cost of some speed. Most of the time this is not required, so it is off by "
"default and should only be enabled in the rare event that you see artefacts "
"when denoising a colour image."
msgstr ""
"抑制彩色影像中可能很少出現的塊狀彩色偽影。此選項分別處理每個通道，並以一定的"
"速度作為代價消除偽影。大多數情況下，這不是必需的，因此預設情況下它是關閉的，"
"並且僅在對彩色影像進行降雜訊時看到偽影的極少數情況下才應啟用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:70
msgid "Color Denoising"
msgstr "彩色降雜訊"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:89
msgid "No secondary denoising stage"
msgstr "二次降雜訊"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:90
msgid ""
"No secondary denoising process will be used. The primary algorithm by itself "
"usually performs well so this is the default."
msgstr "不會使用二次降雜訊。這是預設設定，因為演算法本身通常表現良好。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:99
msgid "Anscombe VST with exact unbiased inverse"
msgstr "精確無偏逆的 Anscombe VST"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:100
msgid ""
"The Anscombe VST is useful when denoising photon-limited images where the "
"noise characteristics are not Gaussian but primarily Poisson or a Poisson-"
"Gaussian mix. It cannot be used in conjunction with DA3D or SOS. Ref: "
"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/5278406"
msgstr ""
"Anscombe VST 對於低光影像降雜訊很有用，其中雜訊特性不是高斯的，而是主要是泊松"
"或泊松-高斯混合的。它不能與 DA3D 或 SOS 一起使用。參考: https://"
"ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/527"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:108
msgid "Data Adaptive Dual Domain Denoising"
msgstr "資料自適應雙域降雜訊 DA3D"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:109
msgid ""
"Use DA3D as a final denoising step. This algorithm uses the output of the "
"primary denoising algorithm as a guide image to perform frequency domain "
"shrinkage on shape and data-adaptive patches. It never produces worse output "
"than the primary algorithm and may improve detail retention and reduce "
"staircasing artefacts. Ref: https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7350835"
msgstr ""
"使用 DA3D 作為最後的降雜訊步驟。該演算法使用主降雜訊演算法的輸出作為引導影"
"像，透過執行頻域收縮對形狀和資料自適應修補。它永遠不會產生比主演算法更差的輸"
"出，並且可以改善細節並減少階梯狀偽影。參考: https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/"
"document/7350835"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:117
msgid "Strengthen Operate Subtract iterator"
msgstr "強化操作減法迭代器 SOS"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:118
msgid ""
"SOS iteration works by iterating the primary denoising algorithm multiple "
"times, each time mixing back a fraction of the noisy image. This can improve "
"denoising performance and reduce staircasing artefacts. Ref: https://"
"arxiv.org/abs/1502.06220"
msgstr ""
"SOS 迭代的工作原理是多次迭代主降雜訊演算法，每次混合回雜訊影像的一小部分。這"
"可以提高降雜訊效能並減少階梯偽影。參考: https://arxiv.org/abs/1502.06220"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:126
msgid "Secondary Denoising Algorithm"
msgstr "二次降雜訊演算法"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:145
msgid "SOS iterations"
msgstr "SOS 迭代"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:146
msgid ""
"Sets the number of SOS iterations. 3-5 is usually a good starting point."
msgstr "設定 SOS 迭代次數。可以從 3-5 開始嘗試。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:159
msgid ""
"Sets the number of SOS iterations. 3-5 iterations usually provides good "
"convergence. Convergence can be seen by examining the updated image noise "
"estimate shown in the log window after each iteration. (These noise values "
"are measured after noise from the original image is mixed back in to prepare "
"the next iteration, so the final output noise level is substantially lower "
"than the intermediate values shown between iterations.)"
msgstr ""
"設定 SOS 迭代次數。3-5 次迭代通常提供良好的收斂性。透過檢查每次迭代後日志視窗"
"中顯示的更新影像雜訊估算值，可以看到收斂。（這些雜訊值是在原始影像的雜訊混合"
"回以準備下一次迭代後測量的，因此最終輸出雜訊水平大大低於迭代之間顯示的中間"
"值。）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:170
msgid "rho"
msgstr "rho"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:171
msgid ""
"rho sets the amount of the original noisy image at each iteration. A higher "
"value means less noise is mixed in, and more of the intermediate result is "
"kept. Values close to 0 or 1 may result in a need for more iterations to "
"achieve convergence at the maximum improvement SOS can produce."
msgstr ""
"rho 在每次迭代時設定原始雜訊影像的數量。較高的值意味著混合的雜訊越少，並且保"
"留的中間結果越多。接近 0 或 1 的值可能會導致需要更多的迭代才能在 SOS 可以產生"
"的最大改進下實現收斂。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:185
msgid ""
"Rho sets the amount of the original noisy image mixed back in between each "
"SOS iteration. Up to a point, larger values will result in greater "
"effectiveness but beyond a certain point the algorithm will fail to "
"converge. The default of 0.2 is often a good starting point."
msgstr ""
"Rho 設定在每次 SOS 迭代之間混合的原始雜訊影像的數量。在某種程度上，較大的值將"
"導致更大的有效性，但超過某個點，演算法將無法收斂。預設值 0.2 通常是一個很好的"
"起點。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:198
msgid "SOS Advanced Options"
msgstr "SOS 高階選項"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:213
msgid ""
"Modulation allows a fraction of the noisy image to be mixed into the "
"denoised result. This may be useful to add microtexture if the denoised "
"result looks artificially smooth. A value of 1 means the output will be 100% "
"denoised, with none of the noisy image added. Modulation is performed at the "
"end of the process, after primary and secondary denoising stages have both "
"completed."
msgstr ""
"調製允許將一小部分雜訊影像混合到降雜訊結果中。如果降雜訊結果看起來不自然平"
"滑，這對於新增微紋理可能很有用。值為 1 表示輸出 100% 降雜訊的影像，完全不混入"
"降雜訊前的影像。調製在過程結束時執行，在基礎降雜訊和二次降雜訊都完成後。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:226
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:238
msgid ""
"Sets modulation. The pixel value is calculated as m * b + (1-m) * orig, "
"where m is the modulation, b is the denoised value and orig is the original "
"pixel value. Modulation reduces the denoising performance, but a little "
"modulation can be useful to add back microtexture to flat regions of the "
"image."
msgstr ""
"設定調製。像素值計算為 m * b + (1-m) * orig，其中 m 是調製，b 是已降雜訊值，"
"orig 是原始像素值。調製會降低降雜訊效能，但稍微調製一下對於將微紋理新增回影像"
"的平面區域很有用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/denoise_dialog.ui:291
msgid "Image Denoising"
msgstr "影像降雜訊"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:30
msgid "Name of the magnitude file: "
msgstr "幅值檔名： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:40
msgid "Name of the phase file: "
msgstr "相位檔名： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:50
msgid "Order: "
msgstr "規則： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:63
msgid "modulus"
msgstr "模數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:76
msgid "phase"
msgstr "相位"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:88
msgid "Centered"
msgstr "中心化"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:99
msgid "Direct Transform"
msgstr "正變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:114
msgid "Magnitude of the image: "
msgstr "幅值檔案： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:124
msgid "Phase of the image: "
msgstr "相位檔案： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:160
msgid "Inverse Transform"
msgstr "逆變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_FFT.ui:201 src/core/command.c:8367
#: src/gui-gtk4/fft.c:148
msgid "Fourier Transform"
msgstr "傅立葉變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:95
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:500
msgid ""
"Select a starless image for recomposing with a star mask.\n"
"    While the primary aim of the tool is star recomposition as part of a "
"star reduction workflow, you can specify any two fits files with the same "
"dimensions and bit depth for blending."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:112
msgid "Star Histogram"
msgstr "星點直方圖"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:113
msgid ""
"Expands to show a mini histogram and transfer function display for the star "
"image"
msgstr "擴充套件顯示星點影像的迷你直方圖和變換函式顯示"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:133
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:540
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:487
msgid "Type of stretch"
msgstr "拉伸類型"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:145
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:552
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:499
msgid "Generalised hyperbolic transform"
msgstr "廣義雙曲變換（GHS）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:146
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:553
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:500
msgid "Inverse generalised hyperbolic transform"
msgstr "反向廣義雙曲變換（Inverse-GHS）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:147
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:554
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:501
msgid "Modified arcsinh transform"
msgstr "修正反雙曲正弦（asinh）變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:148
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:555
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:502
msgid "Inverse modified arcsinh transform"
msgstr "反向修正反雙曲正弦（inverse-asinh）變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:153
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:560
msgid ""
"Select type of stretch. Generalised hyperbolic stretch performs a hyperbolic "
"stretch with parameters for stretch strength, local intensity, symmetry "
"point, and shadow and highlight preservation regions. Modified arcsinh "
"stretch performs an arcsinh stretch with additional parameters for symmetry "
"point, lowlight and highlight preservation. The inverse hyperbolic and "
"arcsinh stretches are also available."
msgstr ""
"選擇拉伸類型。廣義雙曲拉伸使用拉伸強度、區域性強度、拐點以及陰影和高光保護區"
"域等引數執行雙曲線拉伸。改良反雙曲正弦拉伸使用拐點、低光和高光保護等附加引數"
"執行反雙曲正弦拉伸。這兩個拉伸的逆變換也可使用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:166
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:573
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:525
msgid "Colour stretch model"
msgstr "彩色拉伸模型"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:178
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:585
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:537
msgid "Independent channel values"
msgstr "獨立通道值"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:179
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:586
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:538
msgid "Human weighted luminance"
msgstr "人眼加權明度"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:180
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:587
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:539
msgid "Even weighted luminance"
msgstr "均等加權明度"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:185
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:592
msgid ""
"Set the stretch model for colour stretches. The options are: evenly weighted "
"luminance, which calculates the stretch based on a luminance value weighting "
"the R, G and B channels equally; human weighted luminance, which strecthes "
"based on a luminance value weighting the R, G and B channels according to "
"the relative sensitivity of the human eye; and independent channel values, "
"which applies the stretch independently to each channel of the pixel.\n"
"    Note that luminance based models are not generally invertible."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:202
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:609
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:579
msgid "Stretch factor (ln(D+1))"
msgstr "拉伸因子 (ln(D+1))"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:215
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:231
msgid ""
"Independently controls the contrast added (the slope of the stretch) at SP, "
"thus adjusting the amount of stretch applied to the rest of the image. "
"Increasing D increases the intensity of stars in the resulting composition."
msgstr ""
"在拐點處額外增加對比度（拉伸的斜率），從而帶動其餘部分的拉伸量。增加 D 會提高"
"結果中星點的亮度。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:247
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:653
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:622
msgid "Local stretch intensity (b)"
msgstr "區域性拉伸強度 （b）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:260
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:276
msgid ""
"Controls how tightly the stretch is focused by changing the form of the "
"transform itself. Increasing b will increase the intensity of stars with "
"peak brightness above SP, but may bloat their PSF; it will reduce the "
"intensity of stars below SP."
msgstr ""
"透過修改拉伸的演算法，使拉伸力度集中在影像的特定區域。提高 b 值，會提高峰值高"
"於拐點的星點的亮度（但可能會使它們的 PSF 肥大），同時降低峰值低於拐點的星點的"
"亮度。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:291
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:697
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:666
msgid "Symmetry point (SP)"
msgstr "拐點"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:304
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:337
msgid ""
"Sets the symmetry point around which the stretch is focused. For star "
"recomposition, increasing SP reduces the intensity of stars with peak "
"brightness below SP and therefore the amount of stars that show in the "
"resulting composition."
msgstr ""
"設定拐點，即拉伸強度最大之處。對於星點重混合，提高拐點會削弱峰值低於拐點的星"
"點，從而減少結果中的星點數量。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:317
msgid ""
"Allows setting SP from the current selection. This is best suited for use "
"with the background image, where it can effectively pick out faint detail "
"above the background. It is not generally useful with the star mask image."
msgstr ""
"允許從當前選區中設定拐點。適用於無星影像，可以有效凸顯出背景中的闇弱細節。通"
"常對純星影像沒什麼用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:352
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:758
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:727
msgid "Shadow protection point (LP)"
msgstr "陰影保護點 （LP）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:365
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:381
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:771
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:787
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:740
msgid ""
"Sets a value below which the stretch is modified to preserve contrast in the "
"shadows. This is done by performing a linear stretch below LP by reserving "
"contrast from the rest of the image. Moving LP towards SP changes both the "
"scope and amount of contrast reservation, the net effect is to push the "
"overall stretch to higher brightness levels whilekeeping the contrast and "
"definition in the background. This parameter must be greater than or equal "
"to 0 and not greater than SP."
msgstr ""
"設定一個值，低於該值將套用不同的拉伸，以保護陰影中的對比度。在陰影保護點以下"
"的值將改用線性拉伸，其餘部分不變。陰影保護點越靠近拐點，保護的範圍就越大、效"
"果就越強。最終效果是提高陰影部分的亮度，以保護反差和細節。此引數必須大於等於 "
"0 且不大於拐點。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:396
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:802
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:770
msgid "Highlight protection point (HP)"
msgstr "高光保護點（HP）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:409
msgid ""
"Sets a value above which the stretch is modified to preserve contrast in the "
"highlights / stars. The star mask HP can be set to quite a low value to "
"prevent bloat of brighter stars."
msgstr ""
"設定一個值，超過該值將套用不同的拉伸，以保護高光/星點中的對比度。高光保護點可"
"以設定為相當低的值，以防止亮星肥大。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:426
msgid ""
"Sets a value above which the stretch is modified to preserve contrast in the "
"highlights / stars. This can be set to quite a low value in star "
"recomposition mode to prevent bloat of brighter stars while boosting the "
"brightness of fainter ones."
msgstr ""
"設定一個值，超過該值將套用不同的拉伸，以保護高光/星點中的對比度。在星點重混合"
"模式下，這可以設定為相當低的值，用來在防止亮星肥大的同時，提高暗星的亮度。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:441
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:847
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:814
msgid "Black Point (BP)"
msgstr "黑點（BP）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:455
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:471
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:861
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:877
msgid ""
"Black point adjustment. This is a constant value that is subtracted from the "
"image after the initial hyperbolic stretch. BP adjustment may result in "
"clipping the shadows."
msgstr ""
"黑點調節。這是一個常量值，在初始雙曲拉伸後從影像中減去。BP 調節可能會導致陰影"
"切除。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:519
msgid "Background Histogram"
msgstr "背景直方圖"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:520
msgid ""
"Expands to show a mini histogram and transfer function display for the "
"background image."
msgstr "展開以顯示背景影像的迷你直方圖和變換函式。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:622
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:638
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:592
msgid ""
"Independently controls the contrast added (the slope of the stretch) at SP, "
"thus adjusting the amount of stretch applied to the rest of the image. It "
"does not change the shape of the stretch, just the amount, and should be "
"used in tandem with b to control the distribution of contrast and "
"brightness. When this is set to zero, the stretch will be the identity "
"transform, but any ordered black point adjustment will still occur."
msgstr ""
"在拐點處額外增加對比度（拉伸的斜率），從而帶動其餘部分的拉伸量。它不會改變拐"
"點的位置，只是增加斜率，並且應與 b 一起使用以控制對比度和亮度的分佈。當此值設"
"定為零時，拉伸將是恆等變換，但黑點調節（如果請求了）仍會發生。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:666
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:682
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:635
msgid ""
"Controls how tightly the stretch is focused by changing the form of the "
"transform itself. For concentrated stretches (e.g. initial stretch on linear "
"data) a large positive value of b will focus the stretch within a histogram "
"peak while defocusing the stretch away from the peak (such as bright stars). "
"For adjustment of nonlinear images lower or negative values will distribute "
"contrast and brightness more evenly. As a general rule, the value of b will "
"decrease as a stretch sequence nears completion, although larger values "
"(with small D) can still be used for precise placement of additional "
"contrast."
msgstr ""
"透過修改變換本身的演算法來控制拉伸力度的分佈。對於資料密集的拉伸（例如線性資"
"料的初始拉伸），大的正數 b 將使拉伸力度集中在直方圖的峰值上，而越遠離峰值力度"
"越小（例如明亮的星點）。對於非線性影像的調整，較小或負值的 b 將使對比度和亮度"
"分佈更均勻。一般地，儘管較大的 b 值（配合較小的 D）可以用於精準加強對比度，"
"但 b 的值會隨著拉伸操作接近完成而越來越小。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:710
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:743
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:679
msgid ""
"Sets the symmetry point around which the stretch is focused - contrast will "
"be distributed symmetrically around SP. This should generally be placed "
"within a histogram peak so that the stretch will widen and lower the peak by "
"adding the most contrast in the stretch at that point. The stretch will move "
"pixel values away from SP. This parameter must be greater than or equal to "
"LP and less than or equal to HP."
msgstr ""
"設定拉伸強度最大的拐點 - 對比度將圍繞拐點對稱分佈。拐點通常應放置在直方圖峰值"
"上，以便在該點上拉伸出最大的對比度，使峰值變得扁平。拉伸會使得像素值遠離拐"
"點。此引數必須大於等於陰影保護點且小於等於高光保護點。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:723
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:693
msgid ""
"This dropper allows you to set the background stretch symmetry point  based "
"on the average value of  the current selection. This helps in picking out "
"faint detail above the dark background."
msgstr ""
"此滴管可以將背景拉伸拐點設為當前選區的平均數。這有助於凸顯出深色背景上的微弱"
"細節。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:815
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:832
msgid ""
"Sets a value above which the stretch is modified to preserve contrast in the "
"highlights / stars. This is done by performing a linear stretch of the data "
"above HP by reserving contrast from the rest of the image. Moving HP towards "
"SP inreases both the scope and the amount of this contrast reservation, the "
"net effect is to push the overall stretch to lower brightness levels while "
"keeping the contrast and definition in the highlights. This parameter must "
"be less than or equal to 1 and not less than SP. This parameter is generally "
"of limited use for starless backgrounds but is very effective on the star "
"mask for preventing star bloat."
msgstr ""
"設定一個值，超過該值將套用不同的拉伸，以保護高光/星點中的對比度。在高光保護點"
"以上的值將改用線性拉伸，其餘部分不變。高光保護點越靠近拐點，保護的範圍就越"
"大、效果就越強。最終效果是削弱高光部分的拉伸強度，以保護高光部分的反差和細"
"節。此引數必須小於等於 1，且不小於拐點。此引數通常對無星影像沒什麼用，但在純"
"星影像上非常有效，可防止星點肥大。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:900
msgid "Background Stretch Parameters"
msgstr "背景拉伸引數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:913
msgid "Star Stretch Parameters"
msgstr "星點拉伸引數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:941
msgid "Resets stretch parameters for the star image"
msgstr "重設有星影像的拉伸引數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:950
msgid ""
"Applies current stretch to the star image and resets the stretch parameters."
msgstr "將當前拉伸套用於有星影像並重設拉伸引數。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:970
msgid "Resets stretch parameters for the starless image"
msgstr "重設無星影像的拉伸引數"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:979
msgid ""
"Applies current stretch to the starless image and resets the stretch "
"parameters."
msgstr "將當前拉伸套用於無星影像並重設拉伸引數。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:1006
msgid "Log histograms"
msgstr "對數直方圖"

#. gtk_widget_set_visible(lookup_widget("ghtBPcontrols1"), FALSE);
