msgstr "顯示高階拉伸選項"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:1024
msgid "Clipping mode:"
msgstr "修剪模式："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:1036
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/histogram_dialog.ui:438
msgid "Global rescale"
msgstr "全域性重縮放"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:1041
msgid "Select the clipping mode for partially clipped pixels."
msgstr "選擇像素值修剪模式。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/dialog_star_remix.ui:1062
msgid "Star Recomposition"
msgstr "星點重混合"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:51
msgid "Filter Type"
msgstr "濾鏡類型"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:59
msgid "Bilateral filter"
msgstr "雙邊濾波"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:60
msgid "Guided filter"
msgstr "導向濾波"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:65
msgid ""
"Choose filter type. See the documentation for an explanation of the "
"differences."
msgstr "選擇濾鏡類型。每個類型的區別詳見說明文件。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:78
msgid "Guide Image"
msgstr "引導影像"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:88
msgid ""
"Select guide image. No need to select a file if the \"self guided\" check "
"box is checked.\n"
"    WARNING: using guide images that are not based on the original image is "
"likely to produce bad results."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:101
msgid "self guided"
msgstr "自引導"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:103
msgid "Check this to use the current image as the guided filter guide image"
msgstr "選中此項可將當前影像用作導向濾波的引導影像"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:120
msgid "Diameter"
msgstr "直徑"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:121
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:155
msgid ""
"If set to 0, the diameter will automatically be set based on the spatial "
"sigma parameter"
msgstr "如果為 0，直徑將根據空間 sigma 引數自動設定"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:131
msgid ""
"This sets the diameter the edge preserving filter applies over. If it is "
"zero, the spatial extent is set automatically based on the spatial sigma "
"value, otherwise the spatial extent of the filter is set to exactly this "
"value regardless of sigma (spatial)"
msgstr ""
"這將設定邊緣保護濾波器的直徑。如果為零，空間範圍會根據空間 sigma 值自動設定；"
"否則濾波器的空間範圍將設定為該值，而忽略空間 sigma 值"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:142
msgid ""
"This affects the diameter the filter applies over. If it is zero, the "
"spatial extent is set by the spatial sigma value."
msgstr "這會影響濾波器的直徑。如果為零，則空間範圍由空間 sigma 值設定。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:154
msgid "Sigma (spatial)"
msgstr "空間 sigma 值"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:169
msgid ""
"Sets the range of spatial distance between pixels over which the filter "
"operates. A larger sigma means the filter takes into account pixels over a "
"wider area of the image. Note the interaction with the diameter setting."
msgstr ""
"設定濾波器操作的像素之間的空間範圍。更大的 sigma 意味著濾波器會影響更大區域的"
"像素。注意與直徑設定的相互作用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:198
msgid "Sigma (intensity)"
msgstr "亮度 sigma 值"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:208
msgid ""
"This value affects the range of pixel value similarity the edge preserving "
"filter aplies over.\n"
"    If your stars look huge and defocused, start by reducing this value. "
"Depending on your data you may need to make substantial adjustments here, "
"for example setting the value to below 1.0."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:235
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:251
msgid ""
"Modulation parameter set in the [0, 1] range.\n"
"    When this parameter is equal to 1, no modulation is applied.\n"
"    If the parameters is 0, no filter is applied at all."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:270
msgid ""
"Edge preserving filters can be slow on large images, so preview is not "
"active by default. It is strongly recommended to select a Region of Interest "
"(ROI) before activating the edge preserving filter preview."
msgstr ""
"邊緣保護濾波器在大圖上可能很慢，因此預設不啟用預覽。強烈建議在啟用預覽之前選"
"擇一個感興趣區域（ROI）。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/epf_dialog.ui:318
msgid "Edge Preserving Filters"
msgstr "邊緣保護濾鏡"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/extract_channel_dialog.ui:34
msgid "File name for the first FITS file to save."
msgstr "第一個要儲存的 FITS 檔名。"

