#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/savepopup.ui:622
msgid ""
"Note: when embedding ICC profiles libjxl will check if it recognises the "
"profile. If it does, it will set a reference value rather than store the "
"entire profile. This means that when you re-open the file the ICC profile "
"description may be different, although it will be functionally equivalent."
msgstr ""
"注意：嵌入 ICC 色彩特性檔案時，libjxl 將檢查它是否識別該特性檔案。如果是，它"
"將設定一個參考值而不儲存整個特性檔案。這意味著當你重新開啟檔案時，ICC 色彩特"
"性檔案說明可能會有所不同，儘管它在功能上是等效的。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/seqlist_dialog.ui:22
msgid ""
"List of images in the sequence, with their state and quality information. "
"Quality is FWHM when PSF registration is used, so lower is better, and "
"gradient estimator for DFT registration, higher is better. X and Y columns "
"are the translation relative to the reference image."
msgstr ""
"列出序列中影像的狀態和品質資訊。PSF 對位時使用 FWHM，故越小越好；DFT 對位時使"
"用漸變梯度，故越大越好。X 和 Y 兩列為該影像相對於參考影格的平移。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/seqlist_dialog.ui:32
