msgstr "在處理清單中納入/排除選中的影像"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/seqlist_dialog.ui:116
msgid ""
"When toggled, the outline of the reference image as transformed with "
"registration data is drawn on each image to review image position wrt. "
"reference."
msgstr ""
"啟用時，會根據對位資料，將變換後的參考影格的輪廓繪製在每個影像上，以便檢查影"
"像相對於參考影像的位置。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/seqlist_dialog.ui:130
msgid "Reference image"
msgstr "參考影格"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/seqlist_dialog.ui:131
msgid ""
"If set, the current image will be the reference image for registration.\n"
"Only one image can be the reference image in a sequence, setting it will "
"unset the image previously set as reference.\n"
"If not set manually, the first image of the sequence is taken as reference."
msgstr ""
"如果被選擇，當前影像即為對位時的參考影格。\n"
"一個序列中只能有一幅影像作為參考影格，新設定的參考影格會覆蓋之前的設定。\n"
"如果沒有被手動指定，則序列裡第一幅影像即為參考影格。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/seqlist_dialog.ui:143
msgid "Enter the number of the image you want to reach."
msgstr "請輸入影像數量。"

