msgstr "使用檔案頭中的 Bayer 濾鏡排列資訊"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:241
msgid ""
"If this box is checked, Siril will automatically apply the Bayer pattern "
"found in the file's header as well as X and Y Bayer offsets. If the result "
"looks wrong uncheck this box and choose manually your pattern in the Debayer "
"box below.\n"
"    If unchecked, the Bayer pattern given below will be used instead. "
"Warning: to allow SER files converted from films to be demosaiced, "
"monochrome SER will be forced as CFA with the configured pattern."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:252
msgid ""
"Warning: For SER on-the-fly demosaicing, the RCD algorithm is always used."
msgstr "警告：對於 SER 動態去馬賽克，RCD 演算法將一直被使用。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:254
msgid ""
"Due to algorithm constraints more complex demosaicing algorithms cannot be "
"used in the rejection stacking. Our tests also showed that there is no gain "
"in quality when many images are used, while processing time increases 20-"
"fold."
msgstr ""
"由於演算法限制，在帶剔除的疊圖中無法使用更復雜的去馬賽克演算法。我們的測試還"
"表明，疊圖大量影像並不會帶來畫質提升，反而會使處理時間增加 20 倍。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:271
msgid "Bayer/mosaic pattern: "
msgstr "Bayer/CFA 排列： "

