msgstr "匯出 8 點陣圖像時使用："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3550
msgid ""
"Selects which color space to export 8-bit images to, if the format supports "
"ICC profiles. The ICC color profile will be embedded in the file.\n"
"    Note: if the format does not support ICC profile embedding, images will "
"always be exported as sRGB."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3561
msgid ""
"This section contains settings affecting how color spaces are applied to "
"saved files\n"
"\n"
"    These options do not affect the profiles saved in FITS files, which is "
"configured in FITS Options"
msgstr ""

