msgstr "學術式地分配線性 ICC 色彩特性檔案"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3685
msgid ""
"When assigning an ICC image to:\n"
"    * a loaded image that doesn't show stretches in HISTORY\n"
"    * a newly composed image\n"
"    * a newly stacked image\n"
"    assign a linear ICC profile. This is technically correct but generally "
"unnecessary."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3701
msgid "Auto Conversion / Assignment Options"
msgstr "自動轉換/分配選項"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3721
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3750
msgid "Color Matching Functions"
msgstr "顏色匹配函式"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3733
msgid "CIE 1931 2 degree standard observer"
msgstr "CIE 1931 標準觀察者（2 度視場）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3734
msgid "CIE 1964 10 degree supplementary standard observer"
msgstr "CIE 1964 標準觀察者（10 度補充視場）"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3767
msgid "Export built-in profiles"
msgstr "匯出內建色彩特性檔案"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3769
msgid ""
"Export the built-in profiles to the working directory. Elle Stone's profiles "
"are distributed with the CC BY-SA-3.0 licence. As they are built into the "
"Siril binary, this export function serves to comply with the \"share-alike\" "
"provision of the licence."
msgstr ""
"將內建色彩特性檔案匯出到工作目錄。 Elle Stone 的個人資料是透過 CC BY-SA-3.0 "
"許可證分發的。由於它們內建於 Siril 二進位制檔案中，因此此匯出功能旨在遵守許可"
"證的“相同方式共享”條款。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/settings_window.ui:3777
