"Enter the base name of the sequence, for example NGC_6822-L. It will create "
"images in the form NGC_6822-L_00001.fit."
msgstr ""
"鍵入序列的檔名詞根，例如 NGC_6822-L。建立的檔名會從 NGC_6822-L_00001.fit 開"
"始。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_conversion.ui:262
