#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:234
msgid "Minimum Star Pairs:"
msgstr "最少星點配對數："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:248
msgid ""
"The minimum number of star pairs a given frame can have in relation with the "
"reference frame. If a given light frame has less star pairs, it will not be "
"registered."
msgstr ""
"當前影格和參考影格之間的最小配對星點數。如果小於該數，則該影格將不會被納入對"
