msgstr "最多擬合星點數："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:277
msgid "500"
msgstr "500"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:284
msgid ""
"The maximum number of stars to be searched for in each frame (default 2000). "
"The larger this value, the more stars will potentially be detected, "
"resulting in a longer detection but more accurate registration."
msgstr ""
"每影格中偵測星點的最大數量（預設 2000）。該值越大則可能偵測越多星點，會耗費更"
"長的時間並得到更加精確的對位。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:296
msgid "Shift"
msgstr "平移"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:297
msgid "Similarity"
msgstr "相似變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:298
msgid "Affine"
msgstr "仿射變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:299
msgid "Homography"
msgstr "單應變換"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:304
msgid ""
"<b>Shift</b> is a 2 degree-of-freedom (x/y shifts) rigid mapping, well-"
"suited for images with no distortion, no scaling and no field rotation. It "
"needs at least 1 pair of stars to be matched to define the transformation.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Similarity</b> is a 4 degree-of-freedom (one scale, one rotation and x/y "
"shifts) more rigid mapping than homography, well-suited for images with no "
"distortion. It needs at least 2 pairs of stars to be matched to define the "
"transformation.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Affine</b> is a 6 degree-of-freedom (two scales, one shear, one rotation "
"and x/y shifts) more rigid mapping than homography, well-suited for images "
"with little distortion. It needs at least 3 pairs of stars to be matched to "
"define the transformation.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Homography</b> is the default transformation which uses an 8-degree-of-"
"freedom transform to warp the images onto the reference frame. This is well-"
"suited for the general case and strongly recommended for wide-field images. "
"It needs at least 4 pairs of stars to be matched to define the "
"transformation.\n"
"\n"
"<b>WARNING</b>: The initial star matching uses triangle similarity "
"algorithm, in consequence the minimum of star pairs must be at least of 3 "
"for <b>Shift</b>, <b>Similarity</b> and <b>Affine</b> and of 4 for "
"<b>Homography</b>."
msgstr ""
"<b>平移</b>是 2 自由度（x/y 偏移）的嚴格對映，適用於無變形，無縮放，無場旋的"
"情況。需要至少 1 對匹配的星點。\n"
"\n"
"<b>同構</b>是 4 自由度（1 自由度縮放，旋轉和 x/y 偏移）的較嚴格對映，適用於無"
"變形的情況。需要至少 2 對匹配的星點。\n"
"\n"
"<b>仿射</b>是 6 自由度（2 自由度縮放，裁剪，旋轉和 x/y 偏移）的較嚴格對映，適"
"用於較小變形的情況。需要至少 3 對匹配的星點。\n"
"\n"
"<b>單應</b>是 8 自由度對映（預設）。適用於大多數情況。廣域影像尤其建議使用。"
"需要至少 4 對匹配的星點。\n"
"\n"
"<b>警告</b>：初始的星點匹配採用相似三角形演算法，因此至少需要 3 對（<b>平移</"
"b>、<b>同構</b>和<b>仿射</b>）或 4 對（<b>單應</b>）匹配的星點來執行對位。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_registration.ui:323
