"estimate. Helps when ghosted, doubled patches appear in the stack. Alignment "
"points with no successful measurement at all are stacked unfiltered. The "
"warp field engine handles failed measurements itself, by predicting their "
"shifts from neighbouring alignment points."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:694
msgid "Borders feathering [pix]:"
msgstr "邊界羽化（像素）："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:708
msgid ""
"Select here the number of pixels that will be faded out on the borders of "
"each image."
msgstr "在此選擇將在每張影像邊緣淡出(被羽化)的像素數量。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:734
msgid "Normalization on overlaps"
msgstr "在重疊區域套用正規化"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:735
msgid ""
"By default, Siril computes the normalisation coefficients from each image. "
"Ticking this box computes them on overlapping regions instead."
msgstr ""
"預設情況下，Siril 會計算每張影像的正規化係數。勾選此框後，改為僅在重疊區域上"
"計算這些係數，以實現對位。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:748
msgid "Stack stitching:"
msgstr "疊圖拼合："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:766
msgid "Stacking 0 images of the 0 of the sequence"
msgstr "序列位置：0，疊圖影像：0"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1144
msgid "Image rejection:"
msgstr "影像剔除："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1156
msgid "Sequence stacking"
msgstr "序列疊圖"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1182
msgid "Output Normalisation"
msgstr "輸出正規化"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1183
msgid ""
"If you check this button, the final image will be normalized in the [0, 1] "
"range if you work in 32-bit format precision, or clipped in [0, 65535] "
"otherwise. This will work best if you also check Force 32b output, as it "
"will avoid clipping.\n"
"\n"
"WARNING: This option should not be checked for master stacking."
msgstr ""
"如果你選中此按鈕，當以 32 位格式精度工作時，最終影像將正規化為[0,1]範圍；如果"
"在 16 位，則將修剪到[0，65535]範圍。勾選“強制 32 位輸出”可以避免修剪，獲得最"
"好結果。\n"
"\n"
"警告：疊圖主校正影格時不要選擇此項。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1197
msgid "RGB equalization"
msgstr "RGB 等化"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1198
msgid ""
"If you check this button, the channels in the final image will be equalized "
"(color images only).\n"
"\n"
"WARNING: This option should not be checked for master stacking."
msgstr ""
"如果勾選此項，最終影像的各個通道會被均衡化（僅用於彩色影像）。\n"
"\n"
"警告：疊圖主校正影格時不要選擇此項。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1212
msgid "Maximize framing"
msgstr "最大化構圖"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1213
msgid ""
"If you check this button, the final image size will be enlarged to fit all "
"the selected frames of the sequence."
msgstr "如果選中此按鈕，最終影像尺寸將被放大，以適合序列的所有選定影格。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1226
msgid "Interpolation upscaling x2"
msgstr "插值放大 x2"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1227
msgid ""
"If you check this button, the final image size will be upscaled by a factor "
"of 2. This can be faster than real drizzle images obtained during "
"registration but will not produced images as sharp."
msgstr ""
"如果選中此按鈕，最終影像尺寸將放大 2 倍。這比對位期間得到的真正的 drizzle 影"
"像更快，但沒那麼清晰。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1239
msgid "Force 32b output"
msgstr "強制 32 位輸出"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1240
msgid ""
"If you check this button, the final image bitdepth will be forced to 32b "
"even if the input images are in 16b."
msgstr "如果勾選，結果影像會強制為 32 位深度。即使輸入 16 點陣圖像也一樣。"

#. Must be short
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1255
msgid "Save in:"
msgstr "儲存於："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1271
msgid "Overwrite"
msgstr "覆蓋"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1272
msgid "Overwrite file without notice if it already exists."
msgstr "無提示覆蓋已經存在的檔案。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1280
msgid "Start stacking"
msgstr "開始疊圖"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1284
msgid ""
"Start stacking the current sequence of images, using the method and other "
"information provided above."
msgstr "開始疊圖當前序列中的影像，套用上面所選擇的方式和其他資訊。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1296
msgid "Stacking result"
msgstr "疊圖結果"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/siril_stacking.ui:1316
msgid ""
"Stacking of images, either summing, median, mean with rejection or pixel "
"minimum/maximum."
msgstr "影像疊圖，支援加法，中值，基於像素剔除的平均數，或最大/最小值。"

