"resolution OIII image and a half resolution Ha image; upsample Ha upsamples "
"the Ha image by a factor of 2 to match the OIII image; downsample OIII "
"downsamples the OIII image by a factor of 2 to match the Ha image."
msgstr ""
"如何處理所提取的 Ha/OIII 的輸出。無重取樣（縮放）產生全解析度 OIII 影像和半解"
"析度 Ha 影像；放大 Ha 將 Ha 影像放大 2 倍，以匹配 OIII 影像；縮小 OIII 將 "
"OIII 影像縮小 2 倍，以匹配 Ha 影像。"

