#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:63
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:407
msgid ""
"Detect stars in the current loaded image (not sequence image) and compute PSF"
msgstr "偵測當前載入影像（非序列中的影像）的星點，並計算其 PSF"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:67
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:414
msgid "Average PSF parameters for selected stars"
msgstr "所選擇星點的平均 PSF"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:92
msgid "Center selected star"
msgstr "居中所選星點"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:93
msgid ""
"If checked, a star selected from the list will be centered in the display. "
"The current zoom level will not be altered. This does not apply to stars "
"selected by clicking their PSF in the main display."
msgstr ""
"如果選中，從列表中選擇的星點將居中顯示。當前縮放級別不會更改。這不適用於透過"
"在主顯示屏中點擊 PSF 選擇的星點。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:107
msgid ""
"Half-size in pixels of the search box. Only the brightest pixel will be used "
"in this box to fit a star."
msgstr "搜尋框的半徑（像素）。只有框中最亮的像素會被認定為星點。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:123
msgid ""
"Threshold value above the noise for star detection.\n"
"    The median and standard deviation of the image are computed, then the "
"threshold is: median + [threshold] x stdev.\n"
"    The default value for threshold is 1.00. Increasing this value will "
"detect less dim stars, which should be done only when images have a lot of "
"signal or low noise (high S/N)."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:138
msgid "Radius: "
msgstr "半徑： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:139
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:150
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:161
#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:202
msgid ""
"Changes of these four values should be tested on one representative image "
"before using them for registration."
msgstr "在進行對位操作之前，此四個值的改變需要在一幅有代表性的影像上進行測試。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:149
msgid "Threshold: "
msgstr "閾值： "

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:160
msgid "Roundness threshold:"
msgstr "圓度閾值："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:174
msgid ""
"Threshold value of star roundnesses. Decrease this value if stars in the "
"images show small trails, conversely, increase it if they are very round to "
"avoid false positives.\n"
"    The default value is 0.5, suitable for stars twice as big in one "
"direction as the other."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:189
msgid "Relax PSF checks"
msgstr "放寬 PSF 檢查"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:190
msgid ""
"When checked, this button deactivates some checks done at star detection "
"stage, to reject candidates initially detected based on some psf quality "
"metrics. This can be used to force detecting oddly shaped stars (bad "
"guiding, strong coma) but should be used as a last resort, if playing with "
"all other detection parameters fails."
msgstr ""
"選中後，此按鈕會停用在星點偵測階段完成的某些檢查，以剔除原本基於某些 psf 品質"
"指標偵測到的候選星點。這可以用來強制偵測奇形怪狀的星點（不良導星，強烈彗"
"差），但應當在使用其他偵測引數全部失敗時才使用此按鈕。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:201
msgid "Convergence:"
msgstr "收斂："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:214
msgid ""
"Convergence criterion for PSF fitting.\n"
"    Default value of 1 should work on most cases. However for images with "
"strong coma, it may be necessary to increase this value to allow for more "
"iteration steps.\n"
"    This should normally be the case only for stacked images. Increasing "
"this value may signicantly impact star finding computation time."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:229
msgid "Profile type:"
msgstr "形狀類型："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:257
msgid "Minimum beta:"
msgstr "β 值下限："

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:272
msgid ""
"Minimum value for Moffat beta parameter. This can be used to avoid galaxies "
"being modelled as stars with excessively low beta."
msgstr "Moffat 演算法 β 引數的下限。這可以用來避免星系被建模為β值很低的星點。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:287
msgid "Resets all parameters to defaults."
msgstr "將所有引數重設為預設值。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:308
msgid ""
"Maximum star amplitude threshold (stars with larger amplitudes will not be "
"detected)."
msgstr "星點振幅閾值上限（更大振幅的星點不會被偵測到）。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:325
msgid ""
"Mininum star amplitude threshold (stars with smaller amplitudes will not be "
"detected)."
msgstr "星點振幅閾值下限（更小振幅的星點不會被偵測到）。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:337
msgid "Amplitude range"
msgstr "振幅範圍"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:338
