"Enable amplitude range (only stars with an amplitude in this range will be "
"kept from the detection).\n"
"    Note: excluding saturated stars from the list will probably make "
"registration or astrometry fail."
msgstr ""

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:350
