"Maximum roundness, use only to display optical distortions or double stars, "
"not for registration or astrometry, this will break them."
msgstr "圓度上限，僅用於顯示光學失真或雙星，不用於對位或解析（這會破壞它們）。"

#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/stars_list_window.ui:425
